TestHttpRequestJsonBodyAccessibleAsDeepProperty
/ Mock http.request to return a Response-shaped value whose Body is a
/ deep dict. Asserts %resp.Body.a.b% reads through to 42, proving Data
/ Properties navigation works on the typed Response result.
/ (The actual Content-Type → Body parsing pipeline is covered end-to-end
/ in C# by Stage3_HttpContentTypeDispatchTests.cs; this PLang test
/ validates the user-visible navigation half.)
- mock.intercept actionPattern="http.request", returnValue={statusCode:200, headers:{}, body:{a:{b:42}}, duration:"00:00:00"}, write to %m%
- http.request 'https://example.invalid/api', write to %resp%
- assert.equals expected=42, actual=%resp.body.a.b%
